{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, entropy minimization was used to balance the impact of MUL.",
    "The proposed method was applied to GAS (Zhang et al. 2021d), PARAPHRASE (Zhang et al. 2021a), Special_symbols (Hu et al. 2022), DLO (Hu et al. 2022), and ILO (Hu et al. Page 43 of 63 17 2022) as GAS+UAUL (Hu et al. 2023), PARAPHRASE+UAUL (Hu et al. 2023), Spe-cial_symbols+UAUL (Hu et al. 2023), DLO+UAUL (Hu et al. 2023), and ILO+UAUL (Hu et al. 2023).",
    "This paper compared PARAPHRASE+UAUL, Special_symbols +UAUL, DLO+UAUL, and ILO+UAUL with their baseline methods.",
    "The experiments demonstrated the effectiveness of the UAUL method across various templates, as shown in Table 8 and Table 9.",
    "UAUL, combining MC dropout, MUL, and entropy minimization, achieved outstanding performance in the generative ACOSQE task."
  ]
